<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-46-0646 </DOCNO><TEXT>The authors have described an algorithm for solving the Kravtsov equationfor the polarization parameters of a ray (i.e., the equation for thequasiisotropic approximation) simultaneously with the characteristicsystem governing the ray trajectory. Numerical results on the polarizationstructure of quasimonochromatic wave packets are presented for specificmodels of the ionosphere.</TEXT></DOC>